reviewText: Cool as hell. Top quality, great fight card.

This one comes in a group of just ok UFC dvd's.  I don't know if I have seen too many of these or if the current start don't quite have the get up and go of old.  They do seem more professional and appear to be generally better trained, but show biz demands a little crazy as well.  Only 3 star for this also ran.
Really liked it alot but very disappointed that it doesnt  come with their actual theme music.
